VisuBlueDesignOCACmd.Title: Blue Design
VisuBlueDesignOCACmd.LongHelp: This ambience provides a grid, a ground, a sky, a skyline, and no shadow.
VisuDarkDesignOCACmd.Title: Dark Design

VisuStudioOCACmd.Title: Studio
VisuStudioOCACmd.LongHelp:
This ambience contains a ground, a shadow, and a mirror effect.

It is very similar to the White Mirror ambience. The main differences are the reflection map which is more adapted to the review, and the two light sources illuminating the scene (the first one has a warm color in contrast with the second one which has a cool color).
VisuPureWhiteOCACmd.Title: Pure White
VisuPureWhiteOCACmd.LongHelp: This ambience contains a ground, a shadow, and a mirror effect. This is the default ambience.
VisuWhiteMirrorOCACmd.Title: White Mirror
VisuWhiteMirrorOCACmd.LongHelp: This ambience contains a white ground, a shadow, and a mirror effect.
VisuWhiteReviewOCACmd.Title: White Review
VisuWhiteReviewOCACmd.LongHelp: This ambience contains a ground, a shadow, and no mirror effect.
VisuDarkMirrorOCACmd.Title: Dark Mirror
VisuDarkMirrorOCACmd.LongHelp: This ambience contains a ground, a shadow, a mirror effect, and two light sources coincident with the neons which enables to cast shadows on the ground.
VisuDarkReviewOCACmd.Title: Dark Review
VisuDarkReviewOCACmd.LongHelp: This ambience contains a ground and has no mirror effect.
VisuOutdoorOCACmd.Title: Outdoor
VisuOutdoorOCACmd.LongHelp:
This ambience contains a sky, a ground, and inter-object shadows.

As for review ambiences, it uses the SSAO lighting technique.
VisuIndoorOCACmd.Title: Indoor
VisuIndoorOCACmd.LongHelp: This ambience contains a ground shadow, three light sources, and a fuzzy mirror effect.
VisuCityOCACmd.Title: City
VisuCityOCACmd.LongHelp: This ambience contains one light source, a ground shadow, and inter-object shadows.
VisuWhiteExperienceOCACmd.Title: White Experience
VisuWhiteExperienceOCACmd.ShortHelp: Applies the White Experience ambience. This is the default ambience.
VisuWhiteExperienceOCACmd.LongHelp:
This ambience contains a ground, a shadow, and a mirror effect. It also has a background (with a cool area, a warm area, and 2 neon lights).

IBL (Image-based Lighting) is activated with a result similar to the background but with more details and contrast.
VisuRoadOCACmd.Title: Road
VisuRoadOCACmd.LongHelp: This ambience contains one light source, a ground shadow, and inter-object shadows.
VisuQMCommand.Title: Visual Quality
VisuQMCommand.ShortHelp: Lets you modify the rendering performance and the visualization quality.
VisuQMCommand.LongHelp: You can use presets, or customize some visualization parameters through a dedicated editor.
VisuViewPanelCommand.Title: View Modes
VisuViewPanelCommand.ShortHelp: Lets you modify the current view using predefined view modes.
VisuViewPanelCommand.LongHelp: You can also apply default or predefined appearances to your objects, and change the current ambience.
